---

<Layout title="Etobicoke Airbnb Management" description="Expert Airbnb management in Etobicoke. We manage waterfront properties in Mimico, Humber Bay, The Queensway & Islington. 10-15% fees, 9-min response time.">
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="location-badge">ETOBICOKE</span>
      <h1><span class="highlight">Etobicoke</span> Airbnb Management</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">Waterfront living meets convenient Toronto access</p>

      <div class="hero-stats">
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">$3,400+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Monthly Revenue</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">79%+</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Avg Occupancy Rate</div>
        </div>
        <div class="stat">
          <div class="stat-number">10-15%</div>
          <div class="stat-label">Management Fee</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-large">Get Free Property Analysis</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section neighborhoods">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Etobicoke Neighborhoods We Serve</h2>
        <p>Lakefront condos to family-friendly suburbs</p>
      </div>
      <div class="neighborhoods-grid">
        {neighborhoods.map(n => (
          <div class="neighborhood-card">
            <h3>{n.icon} {n.name}</h3>
            <p>{n.description}</p>
            <div class="avg-revenue">Avg Revenue: {n.revenue}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bylaws-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Toronto Short-Term Rental Bylaws</h2>
        <p>What Etobicoke property owners need to know</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bylaws-content">
        <div class="bylaws-grid">
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Registration Required</h3>
            <p>All short-term rentals in Toronto (including Etobicoke) must be registered with the City. The annual registration fee is $55. We can help you navigate the registration process.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Principal Residence Rule</h3>
            <p>You can only operate a short-term rental in your principal residence. This is the home where you live and receive mail, file taxes, etc.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>180-Night Annual Limit</h3>
            <p>Entire-home rentals are limited to 180 nights per year. However, if you rent just a room while you're home, there's no night limit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bylaw-card">
            <h3>Municipal Accommodation Tax</h3>
            <p>A 6% Municipal Accommodation Tax (MAT) applies to all short-term rentals. Platforms like Airbnb collect and remit this automatically.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bylaws-cta">
          <p><strong>Not sure if your property qualifies?</strong> Many Etobicoke condos have additional building rules. We'll help you understand what's allowed and maximize your earning potential within the regulations.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get Free Compliance Check</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section why-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Waterfront Properties Are Our Specialty</h2>
        <p>We know how to market and maximize lakefront rentals</p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Stunning Photography</h3>
          <p>We capture those golden hour lake views that make guests book instantly. Professional photographers who know how to showcase waterfront living.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Premium Pricing Strategy</h3>
          <p>Waterfront properties command premium rates. We price yours to maximize revenue while maintaining high occupancy year-round.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Targeted Marketing</h3>
          <p>We attract guests specifically looking for waterfront stays - couples celebrating anniversaries, remote workers seeking inspiring views, nature lovers.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="why-card">
          <h3>Experience Curation</h3>
          <p>We create local guides highlighting the waterfront trail, Humber Bay Park, and lakeside restaurants that make your listing stand out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section services-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>Full-Service Etobicoke Management</h2>
        <p>Everything included at 10-15%</p>
      </div>
      <div class="services-grid">
        {services.map(service => (
          <div class="service-item">
            <span class="service-check">‚úì</span>
            <span>{service}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Own an Etobicoke Property?</h2>
        <p>Get a free analysis showing how much your Mimico, Humber Bay, or Islington property could earn with Airbnb.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-large">Get Your Free Analysis</a>
        <p class="cta-note">Free consultation - No obligation - Results in 24 hours</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-background-alt) 0%, var(--color-background) 100%);
    padding: 8rem 0 6rem;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: -2rem;
  }

  .location-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 50px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .hero .highlight { color: var(--color-primary); }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 4rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .stat { text-align: center; }
  .stat-number { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .stat-label { color: var(--color-text-light); font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .neighborhoods-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .neighborhood-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-top: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .neighborhood-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
  .neighborhood-card h3 { font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .neighborhood-card p { color: var(--color-text-light); margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.7; }

  .avg-revenue {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .bylaws-section { background: var(--color-background-alt); }

  .bylaws-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .bylaw-card {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .bylaw-card h3 { color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .bylaw-card p { color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }

  .bylaws-cta {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    text-align: center;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
  }

  .bylaws-cta p { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }

  .why-section { background: var(--color-primary-dark); color: white; }
  .why-section .section-header h2 { color: white; }
  .why-section .section-header p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); }

  .why-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .why-card {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .why-card h3 { margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.25rem; }
  .why-card p { color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); line-height: 1.7; }

  .services-section { background: var(--color-background-alt); }

  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .service-item {
    background: white;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .service-check { color: var(--color-primary); font-size: 1.25rem; font-weight: 700; }

  .cta-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    padding: 5rem 0;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content h2 { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .cta-content > p { font-size: 1.25rem; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 2rem; max-width: 700px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }
  .cta-section .btn { background: white; color: var(--color-primary); }
  .cta-section .btn:hover { background: var(--color-background-alt); }
  .cta-note { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.95rem; opacity: 0.9; }

  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .neighborhoods-grid, .services-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .why-grid, .bylaws-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 576px) {
    .hero-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 2rem; }
    .neighborhoods-grid, .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
